-It's doing well.
-Yes.

9
00:01:52,320 --> 00:01:53,759
I'm glad.

10
00:02:00,880 --> 00:02:03,240
Are you sure Director Ma really quit?

11
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:04,720
I don't think he did.

12
