00:51:52,080 --> 00:51:53,800
Why did you want to meet me?

800
00:51:55,480 --> 00:51:58,160
I don't know how much you know.

801
00:51:59,840 --> 00:52:03,160
But I once made a deal
with Lee Hyeong-du regarding you.

802
00:52:03,240 --> 00:52:04,280
And because of that,

803
00:52:05,360 --> 00:52:07,120
I even got investigated by
the prosecution.

804
00:52:08,760 --> 00:52:12,120
What do you mean you made a deal
regarding me?

805
00:52:12,200 --> 00:52:14,600
It literally means I tried
to make a deal with Lee Hyeong-du

806
00:52:16,720 --> 00:52:18,640
regarding you.

807
00:52:21,240 --> 00:52:22,920
What kind of deal?

808
00:52:25,000 --> 00:52:26,200
I asked him

809
00:52:28,560 --> 00:52:31,040
to put you back in the cryonic capsule.

810
00:52:39,280 --> 00:52:41,040
Why would you do something like that?

811
00:52:41,560 --> 00:52:43,120
How could you?

812
00:52:43,720 --> 00:52:46,800
I was still in love
and obsessed with Dong-chan.

813
00:52:47,200 --> 00:52:49,320
And I was jealous of the girl

814
00:52:50,400 --> 00:52:51,440
he was in love with.

815
00:52:55,920 --> 00:52:57,240
You probably wouldn't understand.

816
00:52:59,280 --> 00:53:01,280
I had hit rock bottom.

817
00:53:02,720 --> 00:53:03,920
Did you think

818
00:53:05,560 --> 00:53:07,920
you'd be able to
get him back if I disappeared?

819
00:53:08,000 --> 00:53:09,000
I just wanted

820
00:53:10,120 --> 00:53:12,440
to put him through pain.

821
00:53:15,520 --> 00:53:17,880
He would've had to grow old without you.

822
00:53:18,600 --> 00:53:21,080
And when the woman he loves
shows up still looking young

823
00:53:21,160 --> 00:53:22,600
and neglects him, that'd cause him pain.

824
00:53:25,080 --> 00:53:26,480
I wanted him to feel that pain as well.

825
00:53:31,000 --> 00:53:32,080
Does he

826
00:53:33,560 --> 00:53:34,720
also know about this?

827
00:53:35,560 --> 00:53:36,600
No, not yet.

828
00:53:37,760 --> 00:53:38,800
But he'll

829
00:53:39,960 --> 00:53:41,120
find out soon.

830
00:53:48,320 --> 00:53:49,400
I don't

831
00:53:51,560 --> 00:53:53,080
want him to know.

832
00:53:57,360 --> 00:53:59,080
Let's just keep it between ourselves.

833
00:54:26,480 --> 00:54:28,240
(What are you doing? Are you sleeping?)

834
00:54:32,240 --> 00:54:34,240
(No, I'm outside.)

835
00:54:36,960 --> 00:54:38,800
(Hurry up and come home.
What are you doing outside?)

836
00:54:39,200 --> 00:54:41,160
(I told you not to wander around
because it's dangerous.)

837
00:54:41,680 --> 00:54:42,720
(Where are you right now?)

838
00:54:46,160 --> 00:54:48,240
(Don't worry. I'm in front of the house.)

839
00:54:48,880 --> 00:54:49,960
(I'll be home soon.)

840
00:55:04,000 --> 00:55:05,120
(It's over now.)

841
00:55:06,480 --> 00:55:07,600
(It's all done.)

842
00:55:33,320 --> 00:55:34,760
I fell asleep while waiting for you.

843
00:55:35,960 --> 00:55:37,280
What took you so long?

844
00:55:37,880 --> 00:55:39,080
Where were you?

845
00:55:40,920 --> 00:55:42,120
I met a friend.

846
00:55:43,600 --> 00:55:44,720
That pretty friend of yours?

847
00:55:48,240 --> 00:55:49,240
Just a second.

848
00:55:52,560 --> 00:55:53,560
Here.

849
00:55:56,520 --> 00:55:59,480
What's this?
Is it a tear gas gun this time?

850
00:56:07,480 --> 00:56:08,600
We won't

851
00:56:09,360 --> 00:56:10,800
have to wear this anymore.

852
00:56:11,240 --> 00:56:12,760
Let's hang in there, okay?

853
00:56:16,640 --> 00:56:17,760
It's pretty.

854
00:56:22,320 --> 00:56:25,840
Now that you're wearing that watch,
why don't you reconsider?

855
00:56:26,840 --> 00:56:27,880
Reconsider what?

856
00:56:31,040 --> 00:56:32,240
Do you really

857
00:56:33,200 --> 00:56:34,560
have no plans to get married?

858
00:56:36,920 --> 00:56:38,200
Do you want to marry me?

859
00:56:42,600 --> 00:56:43,640
Then

860
00:56:44,400 --> 00:56:47,000
I want you to wait until I turn 30.

861
00:56:49,760 --> 00:56:52,480
Okay, fine. I guess I have no choice.

862
00:56:55,080 --> 00:56:56,080
It's pretty.

863
00:57:15,280 --> 00:57:17,360
We'll begin the injection.

864
00:57:19,280 --> 00:57:20,720
After a week,

865
00:57:20,960 --> 00:57:23,760
your body temperature
will finally come back to normal.

866
00:57:32,480 --> 00:57:35,320
I heard Dong-chan is
meeting Professor Hwang today.

867
00:57:39,080 --> 00:57:41,720
Is he trying to get the shot first?

868
00:57:45,600 --> 00:57:47,400
Who's that? I thought
I wasn't getting any backup.

869
00:57:54,960 --> 00:57:56,120
Wait here for a second.

870
00:57:56,760 --> 00:57:57,760
Okay.

871
00:58:19,120 --> 00:58:20,600
This is just a transitional phenomenon.

872
00:58:45,240 --> 00:58:47,280
(Bureau Chief, Na Ha-young)

873
00:58:50,680 --> 00:58:51,800
Hey, what's up?

874
00:58:53,400 --> 00:58:54,600
A police car?

875
00:58:55,000 --> 00:58:58,600
Are you telling me
he drives around in a police car?

876
00:58:59,480 --> 00:59:01,640
(Police)

877
00:59:34,680 --> 00:59:36,920
(We'd like to thank Park Jin Young
for his special appearance.)
